"33:10:14" : {s: 33, a: 10, w: 14, r: "ظنن", t: "وَتَظُنُّونَ", l: "ظَنَّ", lc: 47, tl: "wataẓunnūna", lb: "মনে করা, ভাবা, ধারণা/ অনুমান করা",e: "and you assumed", b: "তোমাদের মনে হবে", f: 2, rm: "To think, suppose, doubt, assume, deem, believe, know, imagine, suspect, conjunctive, be sure of something in view of ones observations. As a general rule often this verb is succeeded by anna or an, that means to be sure about."},
"33:10:15" : {s: 33, a: 10, w: 15, r: "اله", t: "بِٱللَّهِ", l: "ٱللَّه", lc: 2811, tl: "bil-lahi", lb: "আল্লাহ ",e: "about Allah", b: "আল্লাহর উপর", f: 139, rm: "to serve, worship or adore; to protect, grant refuge, preserve save, rescue, liberate; object of worship ie God; (ا-ل-ل-ه) God, the one true God applied as a proper name denoting the true god, comprising all the excellent divine names; a unity comprising all the essences of existing things."},
