"33:13:12" : {s: 33, a: 13, w: 12, r: "فرق", t: "فَرِيقٌۭ", l: "فَرِيق", lc: 33, tl: "farīqun", lb: "একটি দল",e: "a group", b: "একদল", f: 12, rm: "to separate/distinguish/divide/split/decide. farqun - the act of distinction or separating. fariq - who separates, discriminates. firqun - separate part, heap. firqatun - band of human beings. fariqun - part/portion, some party or band of human beings. furqan - criterion of right or wrong, draft, evidence or demonstration, a name of The Quran, aid, victory, argument, proof, dawn, distinction."},
